Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.70,0:00:21.66,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:17705,21668}Whenever my feelings were hurt,\NI couldn't see anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.66,0:00:25.58,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:21668,25588}because I held a lie in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.58,0:00:29.55,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:25588,29551}Time moved faster than I could react,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.55,0:00:34.59,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:29551,34597}so I pulled myself away\Nfrom everything, but now
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.59,0:00:40.64,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:34597,40645}I can't stop anything at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.06,0:00:47.61,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:41062,47610}Accepting everything, I rise up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.57,0:00:53.49,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:49571,53491}I'll fly over all of time\Nwhile holding onto your presence,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.49,0:00:56.99,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:53491,56995}following the trace of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.99,0:01:03.00,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:56995,63001}My world becomes engulfed with light.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.46,0:01:09.25,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:65461,69257}A never ending sky,\Nyour never changing eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.25,0:01:12.96,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:69257,72969}I want to love these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.96,0:01:19.35,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:72969,79350}No matter the distance,\Nor if we are separated
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.35,0:01:22.77,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:79350,82770}we are always connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.06,0:01:29.44,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:87066,89444}Want you here tonight!
Comment: 0,0:01:31.11,0:01:31.11,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:91112,91112}Part A
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.66,0:01:39.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:97660,99787}Meimi! Seira!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.66,0:01:44.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:100663,104667}The Tomb Stones are playing\Nat the Portside Concert Hall!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.87,0:01:47.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:104876,107462}– Really?\N– Tickets go on sale today!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.67,0:01:50.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:107670,110506}– What's that?\N– You've never heard…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.71,0:01:52.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:110715,112925}…of the Tomb Stones? They're hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.13,0:01:55.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:113134,115219}Well, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.51,0:01:58.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:116512,118765}You're so dense about these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.93,0:02:01.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:118931,121434}Come with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.10,0:02:08.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:126105,128358}SOLD OUT\NALL TICKETS
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.56,0:02:11.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:128566,131319}I see. Thank you, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.61,0:02:14.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:132612,134822}Too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.28,0:02:18.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:135281,138618}They sold out before noon.\NWe didn't have a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.82,0:02:19.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:138826,139869}Oh, rats.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.07,0:02:23.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:140078,143706}Hey, you girls!\NDid you come to buy tickets too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.91,0:02:25.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:143915,145416}You guys too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.62,0:02:28.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:145625,148419}Too bad. They're sold out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.62,0:02:30.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:148628,150421}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.34,0:02:33.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:152340,153925}She's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.13,0:02:36.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:154133,156761}We should have waited\Nin line last night!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.96,0:02:38.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:156969,158930}It's a school day!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.18,0:02:41.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:159180,161891}– It's only one day!\N– What a bunch of kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.10,0:02:44.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:162100,164268}Rats! That's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.47,0:02:47.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:164477,167355}They're making such a fuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.06,0:02:52.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:168064,172318}DANGER, DO NOT TOUCH!\NSUPER ELECTRIC TRAP
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.03,0:02:58.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:177031,178783}I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.07,0:03:00.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:179075,180243}Hi, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.45,0:03:03.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:180451,183287}Hi, dear. Would you\Nlike some Russian tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.53,0:03:05.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:183538,185998}No, maybe later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.45,0:03:10.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:187458,190753}What's wrong? Why the long face?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.96,0:03:12.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:190962,192839}Don't worry. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.33,0:03:17.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:193339,197427}You sure? All right.\NI'll show you a great trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.63,0:03:21.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:197635,201222}It'll put a smile on any sad face.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.43,0:03:23.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:201431,203224}That'd be terrific.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.94,0:03:33.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:210940,213443}You are now feeling happier.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.90,0:03:39.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:213901,219115}That's right.\NSo happy you want to sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.82,0:03:44.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:219824,224871}Now you feel like laughing.\NYou're so happy, you want to burst.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.07,0:03:50.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:225079,230877}You want to hug your dad\Nfor making you so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.08,0:03:55.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:232086,235840}I think it's working.\NNow for the final touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.04,0:03:58.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:236048,238843}– What?\N– Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.34,0:04:03.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:239343,243306}Tickets to the Tomb Stones concert!\NHow did you get these?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.84,0:04:10.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:243848,250062}A client gave them to me, but I'm\Njust not into loud music like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.27,0:04:12.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:250271,252148}I love you, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.35,0:04:17.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:252356,257695}– They're not good seats, though.\N– That doesn't matter! Thanks, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.86,0:04:19.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:257862,259739}She changes so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.74,0:04:25.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:262742,265995}Two tickets. Who should I ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.91,0:04:30.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:266913,270500}Seira's not interested\Nin this sort of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.70,0:04:36.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:270708,276964}Kyoko and Ryoko would be thrilled,\Nbut they're bound to fight about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.84,0:04:41.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:278841,281928}Sure, he would be happy to go…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.63,0:04:46.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:282637,286349}…but wouldn't it be\Nsort of like a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.52,0:04:54.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:292522,294816}– Catch you later.\N– Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.61,0:04:59.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:297610,299654}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:05.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:302281,305326}– Good morning.\N– Too bad about yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.53,0:05:07.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:305535,307912}I was so upset, I couldn't sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.12,0:05:12.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:308120,312124}You liar, we're late because\Nyou overslept today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.45,0:05:14.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:312458,314168}I'm missing my chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.37,0:05:19.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:314377,319799}– Hey, Emi! Let me see your homework!\N– Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.59,0:05:26.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:323594,326389}Oh, Meimi, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.97,0:05:31.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:327974,331310}– What is it?\N– Well….
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:34.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:331561,334355}If you have something to say, say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.56,0:05:36.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:334564,336816}– I have these tickets—\N– Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.19,0:05:39.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:337191,339443}You're a Tomb Stones fan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.65,0:05:42.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:339652,342196}Why do you wanna know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.11,0:05:49.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:345116,349495}– Tickets to the concert!\N– And front row seats too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.70,0:05:52.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:349704,352832}– How did you get these?\N– From my uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.04,0:05:56.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:353040,356460}– No way!\N– Hey, let's go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.83,0:06:00.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:357837,360381}– How about it?\N– Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.30,0:06:06.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:364302,366137}– Well?\N– Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.76,0:06:08.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:366762,368097}What's with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.34,0:06:10.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:368347,370558}What's with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:20.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:378232,380067}Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.36,0:06:23.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:381360,383613}– What did you want?\N– Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.82,0:06:25.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:383821,385448}Nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.11,0:06:29.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:386115,389535}– You started to say something.\N– Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.74,0:06:31.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:389744,391037}Why the attitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.24,0:06:35.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:391245,395166}Rina will get mad if\Nshe catches you talking to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.16,0:06:38.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:396167,398628}She's got nothing to do with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.83,0:06:41.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:398836,401380}Well, neither do l!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.58,0:06:43.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:401589,403799}What's with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.09,0:06:46.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:404091,406177}What's with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.39,0:06:54.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:412391,414143}May I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.97,0:06:57.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:414977,417605}Forgive me for entering unannounced.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.23,0:07:02.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:418230,422026}That's quite all right.\NDo you have a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.44,0:07:11.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:428449,431494}So you're a sculptor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.70,0:07:15.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:431702,435498}Yes, but I only make metal monuments.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.08,0:07:20.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:436082,440127}Aren't you Daisuke Noguchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.33,0:07:23.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:440336,443631}You were given many awards\Nat one time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:25.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:443839,445633}Yes, I had it good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.84,0:07:29.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:445841,449679}But I've been in a slump\Nfor some time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:34.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:451847,454892}I was recognized as a real sculptor…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.10,0:07:38.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:455101,458562}…only after I made\Nthe Steel Weathercock.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.81,0:07:43.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:458813,463109}Until then, I borrowed a space\Nin a workshop and did odd jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.35,0:07:46.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:463359,466737}All I wanted was\Nto create a masterpiece.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.03,0:07:52.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:469031,472493}But as soon as I unveiled\Nthe weathercock…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:57.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:472702,477540}…my life changed.\NAll my past hardships like a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.20,0:08:04.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:479208,484714}The Steel Weathercock\Nwas my lucky charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:09.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:484964,489969}That's why I wouldn't sell it,\Nno matter how much anyone offered.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.17,0:08:14.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:490177,494348}But it was stolen a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.59,0:08:20.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:495599,500021}And I haven't been able\Nto finish a piece since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.22,0:08:24.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:500229,504108}These past six months\Nhave been particularly bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.31,0:08:27.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:504316,507236}Then recently I learned\Nthat my sculpture…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.40,0:08:30.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:507403,510573}…is being displayed atop\Nthe Misato building.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.78,0:08:33.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:510781,513284}You must contact the building's owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.53,0:08:36.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:513534,516787}Of course I did that! But…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.96,0:08:44.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:522960,524670}Please give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.87,0:08:47.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:524879,527381}The weathercock is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.84,0:08:50.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:527840,530885}I believe you are mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.09,0:08:55.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:531093,535139}I purchased that piece\Nfrom a legitimate art dealer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.34,0:08:58.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:535347,538809}– That's not possible!\N– Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.31,0:09:09.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:545316,549987}That is the contract.\NWell? Now do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.65,0:09:14.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:550654,554450}No, these documents aren't real!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.32,0:09:20.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:557328,560498}If you have complaints,\Ngo to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.70,0:09:24.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:560706,564210}But I warn you, I do have\Nthe documents to prove…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.41,0:09:28.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:564418,568422}…I bought the sculpture,\Nso there's nothing you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.38,0:09:32.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:569381,572676}Unless, of course,\Nyou offer to buy it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.88,0:09:38.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:572885,578265}However, I have promised to sell it to\Na businessman in Hong Kong next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.47,0:09:40.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:578474,580017}So decide quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.51,0:09:43.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:580518,583437}I beg you!\NI'm lost without my sculpture!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.93,0:09:46.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:583938,586190}I must ask you to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.19,0:09:53.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:590194,593114}It's frustrating since\NI can't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.32,0:09:57.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:593322,597368}When will he sell it\Nto that businessman in Hong Kong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.57,0:10:02.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:597576,602373}It will be removed three days\Nfrom now. I don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.29,0:10:06.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:603290,606293}And if he gets the sculpture back…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:10.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:606752,610381}…I'm sure he will be able\Nto create more pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.58,0:10:13.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:610589,613509}But there's not much time left.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.51,0:10:18.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:614510,618305}– Meimi? Meimi!\N– Oh, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.51,0:10:22.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:618514,622726}Are you okay? Since there's\Nno time, maybe we should reconsider—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.93,0:10:28.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:622935,628482}No! If we forsake a person in trouble,\Nwe'll damage St. Tail's reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.69,0:10:32.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:628691,632278}I'll get it back for him at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.23,0:10:37.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:633237,637741}The day after tomorrow.\NThe same night as the concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.95,0:10:41.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:637950,641620}Oh, well.\NIt won't be fun going alone anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.08,0:10:45.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:643080,645666}I wonder what he'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.95,0:10:49.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:645958,649587}Will he go to the concert or…?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.96,0:10:54.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:650963,654925}I can't pull a job\Nwithout giving him a warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.01,0:11:01.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:659013,661140}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.60,0:11:08.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:665603,668564}Asuka!\NWhat time should we meet today?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.27,0:11:12.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:669273,672026}– What are you talking about?\N– The concert!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.23,0:11:14.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:672234,674153}Can't you go by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.36,0:11:18.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:674361,678741}I want you to come with me,\Nor give me back your ticket!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.57,0:11:22.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:679575,682620}Hey! Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.78,0:11:28.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:683787,688667}I will steal the Steel Weathercock\Ntoday from the Misato building.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.87,0:11:30.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:688876,690669}St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:35.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:691921,695758}No, no, no! The concert's today!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.96,0:11:39.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:695966,699970}Forget about St. Tail!\NWe're going to the concert!
Comment: 0,0:11:45.72,0:11:45.72,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:705726,705726}Eyecatch A
Comment: 0,0:11:51.73,0:11:51.73,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:711732,711732}Eyecatch B
Comment: 0,0:11:56.73,0:11:56.73,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:716737,716737}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.48,0:12:00.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:717488,720366}St. Tail, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.95,0:12:03.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:720950,723202}What a bothersome situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.41,0:12:06.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:723410,726914}You must do your utmost\Nto capture her at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.12,0:12:10.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:727122,730334}I'm completing the sale\Ntomorrow afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.79,0:12:13.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:730793,733837}How did you come\Nto own that sculpture?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.08,0:12:17.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:734088,737299}I bought it, of course.\NFrom an art dealer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.54,0:12:21.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:737549,741303}St. Tail never steals anything\Nfrom its rightful owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.51,0:12:25.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:741512,745224}She's just a petty thief,\Nwith no reason for stealing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.43,0:12:28.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:745432,748894}Or are you taking her side\Non this issue?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.10,0:12:32.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:749103,752189}Listen, the mayor and I\Nare close friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.39,0:12:35.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:752398,755234}I can easily have you fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.81,0:12:40.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:756819,760948}By the way, do you mind\Nletting me see that sculpture?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.32,0:12:44.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:761323,764660}By all means. I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.16,0:12:52.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:766161,772084}This isn't good. If St. Tail is\Narrested, they'll know we stole it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.29,0:12:57.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:772293,777047}Not if she can't talk\Nwhen she's captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.59,0:13:07.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:783595,787391}Oh, Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.47,0:13:14.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:792479,794148}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.77,0:13:17.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:795774,797484}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.15,0:13:21.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:799153,801989}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.75,0:13:40.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:816754,820299}May the blessings of God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.80,0:13:43.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:822801,823802}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.01,0:13:48.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:824011,828766}For security, a high voltage current\Nruns through the sculpture.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.97,0:13:51.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:828974,831810}One touch and you're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.51,0:13:55.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:832519,835731}Even St. Tail can't beat that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.19,0:14:01.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:839193,841487}You're insane! She'll be—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.69,0:14:05.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:841695,845074}All it means is a foolish\Nthief was electrocuted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.28,0:14:06.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:845282,846784}That's murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.95,0:14:09.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:846950,849953}No matter. After all,\Nshe is just a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.12,0:14:14.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:850120,854333}– I won't allow that!\N– It's time for you to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.37,0:14:19.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:855376,859171}What are you doing? Let me go!\NHey, did you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.38,0:14:21.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:859380,861673}You won't get away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.34,0:14:29.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:867346,869473}What's wrong, Asuka Jr.?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.68,0:14:33.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:869681,873060}They said they don't\Nneed our protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.85,0:14:37.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:874853,877564}But I'm not giving up that easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.07,0:14:57.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:892079,897376}Funny, no one's around. Maybe\Nhe went to the concert after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.25,0:15:03.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:900254,903340}– Don't do anything, you got that?\N– Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.14,0:15:18.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:917146,918730}Don't touch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.82,0:15:31.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:928824,931034}It's wired with electricity!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.24,0:15:34.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:931243,934037}That fool! Get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.54,0:15:39.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:936540,939960}So that's it! But for now….
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.29,0:15:41.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:940294,941628}Get her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.17,0:15:50.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:949178,950762}It's…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.97,0:15:56.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:950971,956143}…showtime!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.32,0:16:11.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:968322,971992}Stop! You won't get away, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.65,0:16:15.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:972659,975496}– Don't let her escape! After her!\N– Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.25,0:16:22.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:980250,982085}Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.29,0:16:24.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:982294,984087}Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.96,0:16:29.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:987966,989927}She went into quadrant 24C.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.13,0:16:31.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:990135,991929}Shut her in!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.26,0:16:36.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:994264,996391}– Who's there?\N– Oh, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.60,0:16:41.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:996600,1001063}There was no one downstairs,\Nso I just came on up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.48,0:16:43.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1001480,1003315}You won't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:49.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1005984,1009154}Oh, no! I'll be locked in!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.49,0:16:55.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1013492,1015494}Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.58,0:17:02.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1020582,1022125}Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.50,0:17:07.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1026505,1027756}I made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.05,0:17:14.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1032052,1034179}Oh, no, I'm trapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.68,0:17:19.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1036682,1039101}Where is St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.68,0:17:22.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1039685,1042062}I'm sorry, but she escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.56,0:17:24.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1042563,1044773}I believe my son came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.98,0:17:29.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1044982,1049152}Yes, earlier, but he gave up and left.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.07,0:17:34.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1051071,1054700}– Mr. President!\N– It's okay. He's about to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.66,0:17:39.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1057661,1059162}I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.33,0:17:42.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1060330,1062416}Sorry to have bothered you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.45,0:17:46.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1064459,1066503}We've trapped St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.71,0:17:50.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1066712,1070465}Turn the cooler on.\NMake sure it's on full power.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.67,0:17:54.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1070674,1074886}– But Asuka Jr.'s in there too.\N– So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.68,0:18:04.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1081685,1084396}It's freezing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.18,0:18:08.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1086189,1088734}I'm freezing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.56,0:18:11.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1089568,1091028}Put this on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.57,0:18:14.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1091570,1094072}This is for helping me back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.28,0:18:17.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1094281,1097409}You helped me first, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.24,0:18:20.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1098243,1100037}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.41,0:18:23.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1100412,1103874}– You've got a lot of guts.\N– So do you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.25,0:18:29.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1105250,1109171}There's this really headstrong girl\Nin my class too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.37,0:18:33.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1109379,1113091}I don't know why,\Nbut we always end up fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.30,0:18:38.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1113300,1118055}I don't mean to, it just happens.\NWe had a fight today too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.26,0:18:41.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1118263,1121850}– I don't know why, but she was mad.\N– You're so dense!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.51,0:18:45.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1122517,1125812}But I could have been\Nto blame too. Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.73,0:18:51.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1128732,1131360}We've got to do something\Nor we'll freeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.56,0:18:55.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1131568,1135030}– Hey, son, you in there?\N– Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.44,0:18:59.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1137449,1139826}If I can break through that…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.95,0:19:09.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1146958,1149920}– Dad!\N– I knew you were up to something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.12,0:19:12.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1150128,1152172}So where's St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.17,0:19:18.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1157177,1158762}Rats.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.97,0:19:22.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1158970,1162349}Stop! Come back here, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.51,0:19:27.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1162516,1167979}I'm taking the sculpture! Give\Nmy best to your headstrong friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.23,0:19:31.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1168230,1171608}Come back here, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.23,0:19:36.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1173235,1176863}Things look bad.\NNow that Asuka Jr.'s out…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.07,0:19:40.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1177072,1180492}If his father investigates,\Nwe're in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.70,0:19:43.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1180701,1183787}It seems the rumors were true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.49,0:19:47.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1184496,1187290}Your hobby is\Ncollecting stolen artwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.49,0:19:49.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1187499,1189251}That's absurd!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.66,0:19:53.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1190669,1193964}You're not being cooperative.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.34,0:20:00.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1196341,1200679}My God, look at all this!\NThese are all listed as stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.92,0:20:04.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1200929,1204850}You have quite a collection.\NMore than rumored!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.10,0:20:06.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1205100,1206351}Mr. President.
